reviewText: I wanted to love this little Australian film, but didn't. I had a hard time hearing the dialog thru most of the film and not due to any accents but due to the fact that they seemed to talk over each other. The characters were nice and well defined and the story was pretty good too. Just didn't seem to connect with me.
This film is an amazing take on an oft done story. The character exploration and acting makes it an unforgettable cinematic experience.
